message: Failed at least one business validation rules

errors.description: [IRASC5-014]-An Invoice MUST have an Accounting currency code (IBT-006) with value 'SGD', if the Invoice currency code (IBT-005) is not 'SGD'. Otherwise, the Accounting currency code (IBT-006) MUST NOT be provided.
[IRASC5-075]-All currencyID attributes must have the same value as the Invoice currency code (IBT-005), except for amounts expected to be in accounting currency (IBT-006).
